# âœ… ADR-005: Continuous Integration & Delivery (CI/CD)

## ðŸŽ¯ Decision

We adopt **CI/CD automation** for all microservices in the Timeboxing monorepo to enforce consistent quality, enable rapid iteration, and prepare for cloud-native deployment.

We use **GitHub Actions** as our CI/CD orchestrator and Docker-based deployment locally, with the possibility to migrate later to managed services like AWS ECS, GCP Cloud Run, or Railway.

---

## ðŸ”§ CI Goals

* â±ï¸ Fast feedback via automated lint/test/coverage
* âœ… Enforced code quality for every PR
* ðŸ§ª Reliable test & type checking pipelines
* ðŸ” Secure and observable runtime artifacts

## ðŸš€ CD Goals

* ðŸ” Local end-to-end bootstrapping using `Docker Compose`
* ðŸ“¦ Image publishing for future staging/prod environments
* ðŸ§° Infrastructure versioning via Git

